    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李铁拐"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖长锤〗。李铁拐上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "洞府领了众仙命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "兜率宫中走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，李铁拐。只因金母寿诞之期，众仙命我去到兜率宫，请老君写副寿词，也"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好前去祝寿。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凡人都说神仙好，做了神仙也烦恼。好手好脚不肯去，但要叫我跛子跑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李铁拐下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
