          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大和佛） 青鹿衔芝呈瑞草，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐祝愿寿弥高。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿基巩固寿坚牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "展寿席人人欢笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐庆寿诞中，祝寿词妙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红绣鞋） 寿炉宝篆香消香消，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿桃结子堪描堪描。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿曲寿多娇，齐祝愿寿山高。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 长生寿域宏开了，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿烛辉煌彻夜烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众仙如此殷勤，乃我神之幸也。你等随我往凌霄宝殿谢恩去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕洞宾、汉钟离、张果老、韩湘子、李铁拐、何仙姑、蓝采和、曹国舅",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹大唢呐，大小锣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹国舅 （同合头） 愿岁岁年年增寿考。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同笑） 哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
